    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo defines a portion of the Management Information Base (MIB) for use with network management protocols in the Internet community.  This document proposes an extension to the Ethernet-like Interfaces MIB with a set of objects for managing Power Sourcing Equipment (PSE).&lt;/p&gt;</t>
